# Contech Context Routing

- Use the container tag supplied by the human, corpus inventory, or
  benchmark runner.
- Record allowed/default tags in `contech-context.lock` before mounting.
- Mount one clean container for the task.
- Prefer `--clean --ephemeral` for eval and agent usability runs.
- Do not mix corpora in one mount unless the human explicitly asks.
- Hosted answer synthesis is not part of the product retrieval workflow.
